name: Richard Leo Blanco
text: I wish I could say the same. I live in Duterte country, where the resentment against imperial Manila has been generations in the making. In any case, Duterte is a funnel for anger and discontent, so he'll always have the more vocal followers. Never mind the impact of Mar's charisma, or lack thereof.
